{"id":1172,"date":"2025-04-05T00:17:55","date_gmt":"2025-04-04T17:17:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1172"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:41:03","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:41:03","slug":"lan-kim-phi-kim-cang-bong","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/lan-kim-phi-kim-cang-bong\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u0103n kim phi kim c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap t\u1ea1i t\u00e1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng do \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1, tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, da kh\u00f4, da nh\u0103n n\u00f4ng, da l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u00e1i sinh l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o ho\u00e1, ch\u1ea3y x\u1ec7<\/li>\n<li>T\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da<\/li>\n<li>Da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, c\u0103ng m\u01b0\u1edbt, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng thu nh\u1ecf<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>V\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p l\u0103n\/ phi kim c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n cao c\u1ea5p t\u1eeb s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c ma thu\u1eadt Dr.Leemee c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o, tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u00f4ng qua th\u1ea9n th\u1ea5u theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1eabn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1ea3, k\u00edch th\u00edch tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a da.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da kho\u1ebb t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2m n\u00fai, h\u1ea3i s\u00e2m, tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 t\u1ea7m \u0111en c\u00f3 trong t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c ma thu\u1eadt Dr. Leemee<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 3 in 1: T\u00e1i t\u1ea1o &#8211; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i &#8211; b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 1 &#8211; 2 ti\u1ebfng<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 \u2013 05 l\u1ea7n, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 21 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -5px; top: 416.556px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap t\u1ea1i t\u00e1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng do \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1, tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, da kh\u00f4, da nh\u0103n n\u00f4ng, da l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3680,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[34],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1172","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-microneedling","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1172","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1172"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3680"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1172"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\